User Stories
------------
1. When a user logs in they should be able to create an account.
2. At the main page, the user should be able to search the database for a recipe.
3. When the recipes are returned a user should be able to read the recipe and decide whether or not they want to save it to their personal collection.
4. When choosing a recipe, the recipe should appear clearly to the user in its own div front-and-center  and be easy to read.
5. Users should be able to comment on what they liked, or didn't like about the recipe.
